{"tid":2149400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際特赦組織指警針對黎智英　借國安法打擊新聞自由","createTime":"2020-08-10T11:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T12:39:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f62dc7f26a9732ea2b19ed221dcecb3860820a9b","tid":2149400,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542923-20200810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542923-20200810.htm&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=dde907f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542923-20200810.htm&h=485b2deb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542923-20200810.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織香港分會表示，警方以勾結外部勢力等罪名拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英等人士，顯示當局正計劃以《港區國安法》打擊新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n特赦組織相信，黎智英和壹傳媒被針對，與報社批評中國和香港政府有關。組織認為，單純因傳媒機構、出版商或新聞工作者對政府的批評，或者他們的政策倡議而遭懲罰，是打壓表達自由，在任何情況下也不合理。<br />\n<br />\n特赦組織表示，當局暫時未提出勾結外部勢力的具體理據，突顯《港區國安法》這條空泛的條例，可如何被利用打壓政治異見者，促請當局立即撤銷針對壹傳媒和相關人士有關控罪，以及停止騷擾、恐嚇身在香港的記者。"},{"pid":"6e0d689ba3d59db4726cfb75e82e79a9fcd3fd5d","tid":2149400,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ae0be0d1cc80aeb19b741e0fe41a94fe0726b3","tid":2149400,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2001e102c5da387a8c5a834b89370c4d97ef24","tid":2149400,"uid":50386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"國際性嘅非政府機構<br />\n得國際特赦組織係keep住幫香港出聲<br />\n其他淨係一味叫人捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d413271a2f1839ef7f4c50c06c8d6a8154c503d4","tid":2149400,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e189e0b0fd3380b6e15310efa513c0e984a9b72","tid":2149400,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa445d6b9b60555fb2c62bef257ec0d62656d4d","tid":2149400,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f2c2b3724839919732119f01ec899cb7ee7f9f","tid":2149400,"uid":219969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"佢哋幫香港做咗好多嘢，有能力都可以課金支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/74085876272/posts/10157549565681273/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F74085876272%2Fposts%2F10157549565681273%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=ac351562\" data-auto-link target=\"